<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>{{ subject }}</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Base email client compatibility */
        #outlook a {padding:0;}
        .ExternalClass {width:100%;}
        .ExternalClass, .ExternalClass p, .ExternalClass span, .ExternalClass font, .ExternalClass td, .ExternalClass div {line-height:100%;}
        body, table, td {-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%;}
        table, td {mso-table-lspace:0; mso-table-rspace:0;}
        img {-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic; border:0;}

        /* Reset styles */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #2c384e;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        /* Layout */
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .email-body {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        /* Professional elegant header */
        .header-wrapper {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 25px 0 0;
        }
        
        .header {
            max-width: 85%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 22px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.15);
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            padding-right: 20px;
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.15);
            margin-right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            max-height: 32px;
            width: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .header-title {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 4px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c384e;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #6c757d;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        
        .header-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d5f9e 0%, #2c4a80 100%);
            padding: 28px 25px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 0;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header-banner h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .header-banner p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .banner-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 25px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: #fff;
            color: #3d5f9e;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Main content card */
        .main-card {
            margin: 0;
            background: white;
            padding: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.1);
        }

        .card-header {
            background: rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.04);
            padding: 22px 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.08);
            position: relative;
        }

        .status-bar {
            height: 3px;
            background: #3d5f9e;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .priority-tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 25px;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            z-index: 5;
        }

        .urgent {
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }

        .important {
            background-color: #fd7e14;
        }

        .normal {
            background-color: #198754;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 25px;
            color: #2c384e;
        }

        /* Dashboard-style stats */
        .stats-container {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            max-width: 180px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.08);
        }


        .stat-number {
            position: relative;
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #3d5f9e;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stat-label {
            position: relative;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Notification box style */
        .notification-box {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.04);
            border-left: 3px solid #3d5f9e;
            border-radius: 6px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .notification-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .notification-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: #3d5f9e;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .notification-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .notification-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c384e;
            margin: 0 0 5px;
        }

        .notification-message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .owner-highlight {
            color: #3d5f9e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Modern timeline style */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            margin: 35px 0 25px;
            padding-left: 26px;
        }

        .timeline:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 7px;
            top: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 2px;
            background: #e9ecef;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .timeline-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: -26px;
            top: 0;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #3d5f9e;
            border: 3px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .timeline-content {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 2px solid #3d5f9e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #3d5f9e;
        }

        .timeline-text {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2c384e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Modern button */
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3d5f9e;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.2);
        }

        /* Note box with icon */
        .note-box {
            margin: 25px 0;
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .note-icon {
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: 15px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #ffc107;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .note-content {
            padding-top: 5px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Signature & contact */
        .signature {
            margin-top: 35px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .signature-logo {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            padding: 5px;
            background-color: #3d5f9e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .signature-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .signature-text {
            margin: 0 0 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2c384e;
        }

        .team-signature {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            color: #3d5f9e;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f8f9fa, #f1f3f5);
            padding: 30px 20px 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .footer-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .footer-note {
            background: white;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            border-left: 3px solid #ffc107;
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        .footer-note-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .footer-note-text {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .footer-note strong {
            color: #2c384e;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        
        .footer-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.12);
            margin: 22px auto;
            width: 60%;
        }
        
        .footer-info-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .footer-info {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-info strong {
            color: #2c384e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Recipient tag */
        .recipient-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #3d5f9e;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            background-color: rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.05);
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media screen and (min-width: 480px) {
            .email-wrapper { padding: 25px 0; }
            .card-body { padding: 28px; }
            .stats-container { max-width: 220px; }
            .greeting { font-size: 18px; }
            .logo { max-height: 35px; }
            .header-banner { padding: 30px 25px; }
            .header-banner h2 { font-size: 26px; }
        }
        
        @media screen and (min-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper { padding: 30px 0; }
            .header { max-width: 90%; }
            .stats-container { max-width: 240px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
            .header-banner h2 { font-size: 28px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Preview text -->
    <div style="display:none; max-height:0; overflow:hidden; mso-hide:all;">
        {{ pending_modules_count }} {{ modules_text }} en attente - Action requise pour {{ owner_fullname }}
    </div>

    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-body">
            <!-- Professional header structure -->
            <div class="header-wrapper">
                <div class="header">
                    <div class="logo-container">
                        {% if logo_cid is defined and logo_cid is not null %}
                            <img src="cid:{{ logo_cid }}" alt="Logo EDF" class="logo">
                        {% else %}
                            <img src="{{ absolute_url(asset('images/logos/edf.png')) }}" alt="Logo EDF" class="logo">
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="header-title">
                        <h1>Guide du Nouvel Arrivant</h1>
                        <p>Plateforme de gestion des carnets de compagnonnage</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="header-banner">
                    <h2>À valider</h2>
                    <p>Demande de validation en attente</p>
                    <div class="banner-badge">Action requise</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Main floating card -->
            <div class="main-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="status-bar"></div>
                    {% if urgency_level.text %}
                        <div class="priority-tag {{ urgency_level.class }}">{{ urgency_level.text }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                    <h2 class="greeting">Bonjour {{ mentor_firstname }},</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-body">
                    <!-- Statistiques -->
                    <div class="stats-container">
                        <div class="stat-box">
                            <div class="stat-number">{{ pending_modules_count }}</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">{{ modules_text }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Notification section -->
                    <div class="notification-box">
                        <div class="notification-content">
                            <div class="notification-icon">
                                <span>!</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="notification-text">
                                <div class="notification-title">Action requise</div>
                                <p class="notification-message">
                                    <span class="owner-highlight">{{ owner_fullname }}</span> attend votre validation 
                                    pour progresser dans son parcours de formation.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Timeline style info -->
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4 class="timeline-title">Modules en attente</h4>
                                <p class="timeline-text">
                                    {{ number_text|title }} {{ modules_text }} {{ verb_text }} en attente de validation 
                                    dans le carnet de compagnonnage.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4 class="timeline-title">Action requise</h4>
                                <p class="timeline-text">
                                    Une validation rapide permet à votre apprenant(e) de progresser efficacement
                                    dans son parcours de formation.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- CTA Button -->
                    <div class="button-container">
                        <a href="{{ absolute_url(path('mentor_dashboard_index', {'nni': mentor_nni})) }}" class="button" style="mso-hide:all;">
                            🚀 Valider les modules
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Note box -->
                    <div class="note-box">
                        <div class="note-icon">💡</div>
                        <p class="note-content">
                            Votre accompagnement est essentiel pour la progression et la motivation de {{ owner_fullname }}.
                            Chaque validation est une étape importante dans son développement professionnel.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Signature -->
                    <div class="signature">
                        <div class="signature-logo">GNA</div>
                        <div class="signature-content">
                            <p class="signature-text">Cordialement,</p>
                            <p class="team-signature">L'équipe de gestion des carnets de compagnonnage.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Footer -->  
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-top">
                    <div class="footer-note">
                        <span class="footer-note-icon">⚠️</span>
                        <div class="footer-note-text">
                            <strong>Message automatique</strong>
                            Envoyé chaque mercredi à 14h00
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-divider"></div>
                
                <div class="footer-info-wrapper">
                    <div class="footer-info">
                        <strong>Merci de ne pas répondre directement à cet email.</strong>
                        Pour toute assistance concernant les carnets de compagnonnage, contactez notre équipe support.
                    </div>
                    
                    {# <div class="footer-links">
                        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Aide</a>
                        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contact</a>
                        <a href="#" class="footer-link">FAQ</a>
                    </div> #}
                    
                    <div class="recipient-tag">{{ mentor_email }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>